{"Sid":0,"Did":25512,"Id":"312438","Title":"劉宇邦訪談錄","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collection/2020-01-04/476b9e9b-081a-44df-8956-be4d1093b654/p3.20-DSC_3569.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collection/2020-01-04/9c9daf4e-7288-43cd-913f-a958aa9da70d/p3.20-DSC_3566.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n劉宇邦為來臺移民的第三代，民國60年1月23日出生，祖籍為河南省開封縣人，岡山出生。其祖父為空軍的土官，於民國37年隨國民黨軍隊來臺，當時落腳於岡山一帶，但後來祖父因宗教的關係，遭到部隊開除，後為了養家的關係，開始改良來自四川家鄉的豆瓣醬，因當時剛好遇到了謝東閔的「家庭即工廠」，即開始利用家庭辦理豆瓣醬工廠，並沿著眷村叫賣，在岡山一帶眷村相當有名。\n\n劉宇邦的訪談錄，主要說明岡山豆瓣醬為何有名，其生成自有其歷史背景。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"NULL","Keyword_Latitude":"NULL","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/17F08565-FF38-45A3-AAE1-F508BE6DC998","Original_Identifier":"312438","Keyword_Subject_1":"社會與政治","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"豆瓣醬 / 岡山眷村 / 眷村文化","dates":"創作時間 / 2019/07/05","LastUpdateTime":"2020/01/04 17:00:06","Creator":"顧超光、楊双福","publisher":"","mediaType":"文件","language":"","timelines":"戰後時期 (1945~)","city":"高雄市岡山區","address":"","lng":"","lat":"","contributors":"","contributor":"顧超光、楊双福","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"高雄市政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collectionOpen/2020-01-04/0488693b-9112-4b92-8aab-6a7dba5dc7bb/p3.20-DSC_3569.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/collectionOpen/2020-01-04/fe8ee20b-5e8c-4102-a688-1d5087984575/p3.20-DSC_3566.jpg"}}